{
  "stem": "18056.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 323.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They marched in with all their ammunition and-- and guns and horses and cars and trucks and whatever.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We-- we were-- we were amazed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, the propaganda in Poland, they thought, well, Germany, three, four days, the Polacks can take Berlin.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, it was just the other way around.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, in a few days, 10 days, the-- the German army was outside of Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we went back to Konstantynow after the war was over, the Germans came in.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the problem was, in these little towns, you were able to maybe manage better as far as food is concerned, because we had so many good friends-- we thought they are good friends, the Polacks-- and we thought that maybe, you know, we would be able to get a bread and sell it in Lodz.",
      "word_count": 56
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And maybe we will have half of the bread.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Our-- our financial situation was not very good at the time, because my father was not there and my mother had to take care of two kids.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So me, as a-- as a boy at the time of 14 and 1/2 years old, I tried to do the things that a husband would do, as far as buying and selling something and, you know, trying to earn some money.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "School was over with the-- the day the war started.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was finished.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not all over.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not all over.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But in some cases, it was chaos.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Fathers would run away.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Mothers would run away.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Kids would run away.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, it was-- nobody realized that there is such a blitzkrieg, that the Germans are so strong and so fast that they could take Poland in-- practically in a week or 10 days.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Nobody realized that.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
